WEBVTT

00:48.591 --> 00:56.682
THE DEAL

01:10.237 --> 01:15.451
Honey... I need your help...

01:18.287 --> 01:23.501
Honey. Help me, please.

01:25.753 --> 01:27.463
Help me, please.

01:27.505 --> 01:31.467
No. Baby! Baby.

01:31.509 --> 01:33.469
It's okay. It's okay.

01:33.511 --> 01:34.970
Here, I'll take you to a hospital.

01:35.012 --> 01:37.515
It's okay. Here.

01:38.224 --> 01:40.017
Come on, baby. There. Get in.

01:41.769 --> 01:44.522
I'm here, baby. It's okay.

02:12.049 --> 02:14.552
It's my fault. It's all my fault.

02:16.262 --> 02:18.556
It's okay. Look, it's the police.

02:18.931 --> 02:20.015
Don't worry,

02:20.057 --> 02:23.018
everything's gonna be okay.
Officer!

02:27.064 --> 02:31.026
So, you're saying
it was a break-in?

02:31.068 --> 02:32.319
Yes, right.

02:34.071 --> 02:35.322
Can I go with her, please?

02:35.364 --> 02:38.075
Sure, after a few more questions.

02:38.576 --> 02:40.744
You said they broke in
in the afternoon.

02:40.786 --> 02:43.330
Yes. No. First, a girl came by.

02:43.372 --> 02:46.000
Curly blond hair,
she was wearing a jacket,

02:46.041 --> 02:48.043
and said that she was
in a car accident,

02:48.085 --> 02:49.044
and that there was no signal.

02:49.086 --> 02:51.630
There was signal at our house,
so she came in, ate something,

02:51.672 --> 02:53.257
and we waited for her mother
to pick her up.

02:53.591 --> 02:54.550
Her mother.

02:54.592 --> 02:56.552
Yes, at least that's what she said.

02:56.594 --> 02:59.096
But one thing led to another--

03:01.098 --> 03:04.351
I'm sorry, what do you mean
one thing lead to another?

03:08.105 --> 03:10.566
Can I go with my wife now?

03:10.608 --> 03:13.652
Yo! The car's documents.

03:13.694 --> 03:14.862
Last name?

03:14.904 --> 03:16.572
Riscal. Mr. Riscal.

03:16.614 --> 03:17.573
Riscal.

03:17.615 --> 03:19.116
-Where are you taking her?
-Don't worry.

03:19.366 --> 03:20.576
She will be okay.

03:20.618 --> 03:22.244
She's okay. She's stable.

03:22.286 --> 03:23.579
We will keep you informed,

03:23.621 --> 03:27.082
but you need to come
to the police station.

03:27.124 --> 03:28.083
Who? Me?

03:28.125 --> 03:29.627
Please.

03:30.836 --> 03:32.087
Please.

03:33.881 --> 03:35.633
Come with us.

03:44.475 --> 03:46.101
24 HOURS EARLIER

03:46.143 --> 03:48.646
No, I want her out.

03:49.647 --> 03:51.106
She can't have a say.

03:51.148 --> 03:53.108
Okay, anything else?

03:53.150 --> 03:55.277
I want to be the majority shareholder.

03:55.319 --> 03:58.155
I want full control over the Board.

03:58.656 --> 04:00.115
And most importantly,

04:00.157 --> 04:02.117
I want her to be forced to attend

04:02.159 --> 04:03.619
whenever I call her.

04:03.661 --> 04:06.080
I want her to look me in the eye
when I have something to say.

04:06.455 --> 04:07.581
That's going to be challenging.

04:07.623 --> 04:09.124
I don't give a fuck.

04:09.166 --> 04:11.335
You're my lawyer
and these are my terms.

04:11.377 --> 04:13.087
If that's what you want--

04:13.128 --> 04:15.297
Can she decline?

04:15.339 --> 04:19.468
Borja, you two spent a decade
building the company.

04:19.510 --> 04:21.637
She should have considered
that before... Fuck it.

04:21.679 --> 04:23.555
Borja, listen. Cat is very smart.

04:23.597 --> 04:25.849
Since she came to the firm
with her father

04:25.891 --> 04:27.643
and stayed with us in the office,

04:27.685 --> 04:29.061
she never said a word,

04:29.103 --> 04:31.146
but I'm sure she perfectly understood

04:31.188 --> 04:34.650
every time we talked about
mergers and acquisitions.

04:34.692 --> 04:36.777
Her father never hid
anything from her.

04:36.819 --> 04:39.154
On the contrary,
he wanted her to be prepared

04:39.196 --> 04:40.656
for the future.

04:40.698 --> 04:41.657
I know.

04:43.701 --> 04:46.328
So while I review these bylaws,

04:46.370 --> 04:49.123
you try to work it out calmly.

04:49.707 --> 04:53.168
Dammit. Seven years thrown away.

04:53.210 --> 04:55.379
We will use that in our lawsuit.

04:55.421 --> 04:59.425
Look, if she declines our offer,
we will file for divorce.

04:59.466 --> 05:03.554
We will allege breach of trust
and betrayal of vows,

05:04.221 --> 05:06.181
saying that it all occurred
behind your back

05:06.223 --> 05:10.394
while you worked relentlessly
trying to establish the company.

05:10.436 --> 05:12.354
There's no way a judge
won't find an aggravating factor

05:12.396 --> 05:16.233
when the relationship between you
is also proven.

05:17.484 --> 05:21.697
We will threaten her with damaging
her reputation on social media

05:21.739 --> 05:22.948
and everywhere else.

05:22.990 --> 05:24.199
Will it work?

05:24.241 --> 05:26.744
Of course. I'm sure it will.

05:27.244 --> 05:30.205
I'm only worried about
the eighth clause of the deal.

05:30.247 --> 05:33.709
It could backfire in trial, Borja.

05:33.751 --> 05:36.712
It's unusual. It's... excessive.

05:36.754 --> 05:39.214
We need something big

05:39.256 --> 05:42.426
to make sense of your state of mind.

05:42.468 --> 05:44.511
So, do you have any proof
or something?

05:45.262 --> 05:47.264
Sure. Hold on.

05:48.766 --> 05:52.770
I will send you some pictures.
Don't hang up.

05:59.985 --> 06:02.780
They're on their way.

06:04.782 --> 06:06.950
Yes, I see them.

06:06.992 --> 06:09.244
Oh, shit.

06:09.286 --> 06:11.455
You full-on caught her, man.

06:11.789 --> 06:14.291
One more thing,
thank you for choosing me.

06:14.541 --> 06:17.252
No. No, it's nothing.

06:17.294 --> 06:21.799
Listen to me...
don't lose your head, alright?

06:22.049 --> 06:24.760
Don't get swept up by your emotions
and end up doing something

06:24.802 --> 06:26.929
you might regret
for the rest of your life.

06:26.970 --> 06:30.265
No, I won't. I will call you
when everything is over.

06:30.307 --> 06:33.310
Fine. Bye, man.

06:43.821 --> 06:45.322
Do you know who she is?

06:51.537 --> 06:55.124
Yes. She's my wife.

06:56.041 --> 06:57.793
With someone I know.

06:57.835 --> 07:00.295
We found these in your house,
along with--

07:00.337 --> 07:02.589
-So?
-Let me finish.

07:02.631 --> 07:04.842
Right. I'm sorry.

07:05.342 --> 07:07.636
Did you file for divorce?

07:09.054 --> 07:12.307
These pictures made you
take action?

07:12.349 --> 07:14.309
I sent them to my lawyer
for advice.

07:14.351 --> 07:17.312
Answer the question.

07:17.354 --> 07:19.815
Not without my lawyer.

07:19.857 --> 07:22.651
Tell me what happened last night.

07:23.861 --> 07:26.822
Well--

07:26.864 --> 07:28.824
Hey there.

07:28.866 --> 07:30.325
What's up, man?

07:30.367 --> 07:31.326
You're on your way, right?

07:31.368 --> 07:34.371
Yeah, I just made a stop.
Do you need anything?

07:34.830 --> 07:37.624
Not at all.
There's plenty of everything.

07:39.668 --> 07:41.336
Are you okay?

07:42.379 --> 07:44.548
Yes, of course. Why?

07:44.590 --> 07:46.049
I don't know.
It's your anniversary, right?

07:46.091 --> 07:47.843
I have nothing to do with it.

07:47.885 --> 07:50.345
You're my best pal, aren't you?

07:50.387 --> 07:53.348
I mean... this should be
between you two.

07:53.390 --> 07:54.850
She's on a trip.

07:54.892 --> 07:56.351
On your anniversary?

07:56.393 --> 07:59.354
Yes. You know, duty calls.

07:59.396 --> 08:01.315
-So, what did you get her?
-What?

08:01.356 --> 08:03.859
For a present,
what did you get her?

08:03.901 --> 08:06.862
Honestly, I didn't find
anything she would like.

08:06.904 --> 08:09.865
But maybe you can help me
to find her something.

08:09.907 --> 08:14.578
You know her almost
as well as I do. Huh?

08:14.620 --> 08:15.412
Sure.

08:16.246 --> 08:19.374
We will find something.
Don't you worry.

08:19.875 --> 08:22.377
Okay. One more thing.

08:22.419 --> 08:24.838
I'm glad you're coming this weekend.

08:25.380 --> 08:28.383
We'll have a good time.
I needed a weekend with friends.

08:28.425 --> 08:29.676
You know.

08:29.718 --> 08:31.720
In the end, it's always
only you and me.

08:33.222 --> 08:34.556
I'm on my way.

08:34.598 --> 08:36.892
Good, drive safely.

09:02.459 --> 09:03.418
You're here.

09:03.460 --> 09:05.420
Sure, where else would I be?

09:05.462 --> 09:06.964
Come here.

09:10.259 --> 09:12.135
Oh! You cooked.

09:12.177 --> 09:14.471
I did. Smell.

09:16.473 --> 09:19.476
Look at this.

09:21.728 --> 09:23.438
Tasty, right?

09:23.480 --> 09:25.482
It's been a while since
you last cooked for me.

09:27.109 --> 09:28.944
Can I take a shower before dinner?

09:29.194 --> 09:31.989
Of course. Today's your day.

09:32.489 --> 09:36.994
It's so good. Delicious.

09:45.502 --> 09:47.963
Margaux '59.

09:48.005 --> 09:51.466
Weren't we keeping it
for a special occasion?

09:51.508 --> 09:53.969
We're always keeping things
for special occasions.

09:54.011 --> 09:58.015
What better occasion than
celebrating our marriage?

09:59.683 --> 10:06.148
Here. Also, you said you wanted
to explore the limits, right?

10:06.189 --> 10:10.527
-Me?
-Yes. You.

10:17.534 --> 10:21.538
To us. To you.

10:35.052 --> 10:37.054
Let me taste it.

11:38.115 --> 11:40.117
The doorbell.

11:49.876 --> 11:52.129
Are you expecting anyone?

11:52.921 --> 11:58.135
Could it be flowers
or an anniversary gift?

11:58.635 --> 11:59.553
What are you doing here?

11:59.594 --> 12:02.639
-Weren't you on a trip?
-A trip?

12:07.144 --> 12:09.271
Marcos, it's nice to see you.

12:09.312 --> 12:11.606
What a surprise, come in.
Come in.

12:11.648 --> 12:17.112
-Honey!
-Marcos, you're here!

12:17.154 --> 12:18.113
Please, come in.

12:18.155 --> 12:20.115
Cat was about to take a shower.

12:20.157 --> 12:21.116
Dinner is ready.

12:21.158 --> 12:23.660
I opened a wonderful wine.
You will like it.

12:23.910 --> 12:26.163
Terrific.

12:26.663 --> 12:28.623
Help yourself. I'm coming.

12:28.665 --> 12:32.127
Can you explain me
why you invited Marcos?

12:32.169 --> 12:35.088
Well, I told you today
I was feeling spontaneous.

12:35.130 --> 12:36.381
And you said you liked that.

12:37.174 --> 12:41.178
Relax, we will have fun.
You'll see.

12:52.689 --> 12:55.358
Dear Lord, you're a great cook, bud.

12:55.400 --> 12:56.985
Fuck.

12:58.695 --> 13:00.655
I think I overate.

13:00.697 --> 13:03.450
I'm glad. Bud.

13:03.700 --> 13:06.661
Actually, you've always
been a great cook.

13:06.703 --> 13:09.206
I still don't know what the hell
I'm doing here, but--

13:09.498 --> 13:12.209
After this, I won't complain, right?

13:13.210 --> 13:14.669
To us, guys.

13:14.711 --> 13:16.213
We're glad you're here.

13:16.463 --> 13:18.381
Yes. That's true.

13:18.423 --> 13:25.222
To my best, best, best,
best friend.

13:30.519 --> 13:34.231
Seven years later, here we are.
The three of us.

13:34.731 --> 13:37.234
It seems like it was yesterday,
the biggest drinking night ever.

13:38.235 --> 13:41.738
And here we are. The three of us.

13:46.243 --> 13:48.203
It was a lovely wedding.

13:48.870 --> 13:52.207
I almost forgot.
There's one more thing.

13:52.249 --> 13:54.209
I can't eat anything else.
Or I might throw up.

13:54.251 --> 13:56.253
Trust me, you will love this.

13:59.756 --> 14:01.758
Please, find a way to leave, okay?

14:02.008 --> 14:04.219
I don't know what's going on,
but this is awkward,

14:04.261 --> 14:07.264
so find an excuse to leave.

14:09.891 --> 14:13.853
Let's see what the chef prepared.

14:14.271 --> 14:15.730
VoilÃ !

14:15.772 --> 14:18.233
-What's this?
-Dessert.

14:18.275 --> 14:22.237
This is for you.
And this one is yours.

14:22.279 --> 14:24.281
Enjoy, pal.

14:31.079 --> 14:34.749
Non-disclosure agreement.
What is it for?

14:34.791 --> 14:37.377
Are you creating a new company or--

14:40.213 --> 14:42.257
This motherfucker is funny.

14:42.299 --> 14:44.259
Always thinking of business, huh?

14:44.301 --> 14:46.303
I don't understand
what the fuck is this.

14:46.595 --> 14:51.808
It's something special.
To my most special persons.

14:52.309 --> 14:56.271
No, it's not that. This has
nothing to do with business.

14:56.313 --> 14:57.772
This is about us.

14:58.023 --> 15:01.276
It is. But it's not.

15:01.318 --> 15:02.819
But it is.

15:03.528 --> 15:07.282
It's about you. About all of us.

15:07.324 --> 15:09.284
And our business.

15:16.333 --> 15:18.084
Well, I better get going, or--

15:18.126 --> 15:21.296
-It's too late for that, you moron.
-Is it?

15:21.338 --> 15:23.298
This is between you two,
I'm leaving.

15:23.340 --> 15:28.345
This actually concerns you.

15:28.845 --> 15:30.513
Stop pretending, I know it all.

15:30.555 --> 15:33.266
I've seen your photographs,
everything.

15:33.850 --> 15:35.310
How can you be so cynical?

15:35.352 --> 15:36.853
Are you losing it or what?

15:37.103 --> 15:39.814
-Cynical me?
-Yes, you.

15:40.357 --> 15:42.817
What's this? The divorce papers?

15:42.859 --> 15:45.987
No. No, no, it's--

15:46.029 --> 15:48.823
It's a deal, he wants to buy me out.

15:48.865 --> 15:50.367
What?

15:50.867 --> 15:53.662
Let's call it a practical divorce.

15:54.079 --> 15:55.288
As set forth herein,

15:55.330 --> 15:58.333
I'll gain control
of your shares and the company.

15:58.375 --> 16:02.962
And listen, I'm paying you
enough money so you can do

16:03.004 --> 16:04.839
whatever you want,
wherever you want to do it.

16:04.881 --> 16:07.342
That way, I can leave you behind,
and keep my company.

16:07.384 --> 16:10.303
Down here, on Earth,
I will do that.

16:10.345 --> 16:12.347
A campaign to rename the brand.

16:12.389 --> 16:13.848
You will fade out gradually.

16:13.890 --> 16:15.809
No complications, no drama,
nothing.

16:15.850 --> 16:18.645
You two can stop hiding like rats.

16:18.687 --> 16:21.356
And I can continue working
on the company I built.

16:21.398 --> 16:22.857
That we both built.

16:22.899 --> 16:25.193
Look, you lost
the right to say that

16:25.235 --> 16:26.861
the moment you started
fucking with my best pal.

16:26.903 --> 16:29.614
One thing has nothing to do
with the other.

16:30.156 --> 16:32.033
You're playing the victim now?

16:32.075 --> 16:35.370
I'm the victim here. Understood?

16:35.412 --> 16:37.831
And let me tell you this,
be smart.

16:37.872 --> 16:40.375
Any other man,
under these circumstances,

16:40.417 --> 16:43.378
wouldn't even give you
half the money I'm offering.

16:43.420 --> 16:45.839
-Don't play the fucking victim.
-Take it easy, okay?

16:45.880 --> 16:47.382
-Shut up.
-I can't speak?

16:47.424 --> 16:50.176
Then what the fuck am I doing here?
Huh? Tell me.

17:00.228 --> 17:02.439
I want you two to look me in the eye.

17:03.440 --> 17:06.609
After all of this, after so long,

17:06.651 --> 17:09.070
and so much bullshit and lies,

17:09.112 --> 17:11.698
I'm trying to be the bigger man.

17:11.740 --> 17:14.159
Okay. I'll get going, or--

17:14.200 --> 17:15.410
Are you leaving her alone?

17:15.452 --> 17:17.537
You fucked her all this time,
and now you're leaving her?

17:18.955 --> 17:21.958
I'm freaking out
about all of this too!

17:31.468 --> 17:34.971
Was there someone else
when all of this happened?

17:35.680 --> 17:38.433
Um... yes. Marcos, a friend.

17:38.475 --> 17:40.477
Marcos, right.

17:41.478 --> 17:44.647
Mr. Riscal, you better cooperate
and don't lie to me.

17:45.482 --> 17:47.942
Listen, lady.
I'm telling the truth.

17:47.984 --> 17:51.154
Your house was intact.
There were no sings of a break-in.

17:51.196 --> 17:53.656
We only found
your wife's suitcase.

17:56.159 --> 17:57.118
What about Marcos?

17:57.494 --> 17:58.995
What do you want me to tell you?

17:59.245 --> 18:02.999
-I did wrong.
-So wrong.

18:04.417 --> 18:06.002
Look...

18:10.006 --> 18:12.717
For some reason, at some point

18:12.759 --> 18:16.471
in life you forgot about me,
you replaced me.

18:16.513 --> 18:19.015
Do you realize that much?

18:20.517 --> 18:23.478
Maybe you didn't notice,
but all the energy that we had,

18:23.520 --> 18:26.731
all the energy between us,
you poured it all on our company.

18:26.773 --> 18:30.693
You and I became nothing
but a business.

18:30.735 --> 18:32.779
And you forgot about me.

18:32.821 --> 18:37.534
You're a man of success.
You don't like failure.

18:38.034 --> 18:41.037
That's why I never thought
this would happen.

18:41.538 --> 18:45.041
I thought we could survive
this, do you hear me?

18:45.834 --> 18:48.461
All of a sudden, those trips started.

18:48.503 --> 18:50.505
What first were getaway trips,

18:50.547 --> 18:52.674
suddenly became business trips.

18:52.715 --> 18:54.551
Longer and longer and longer trips,

18:54.801 --> 18:56.010
and we were so fucked up.

18:56.052 --> 18:59.013
As fucked up as everybody else.

18:59.055 --> 19:01.516
We became the common denominator.

19:01.558 --> 19:04.018
All the lies and the betrayal,
and that sort of things,

19:04.060 --> 19:07.522
and this fucking house where
I thought we would finally be alone,

19:07.564 --> 19:11.025
just you and me,
and get back what we had,

19:11.067 --> 19:15.071
but it turned out that I
was left all alone. Do you realize?

19:20.577 --> 19:25.081
You're good, huh? No. I don't know
why but I don't believe you.

19:25.582 --> 19:30.086
Oh. Right. Wait. Look at this.

19:34.090 --> 19:36.593
No, no, wait. Look.

19:38.094 --> 19:40.096
Okay, stop it now.

19:45.101 --> 19:47.562
You will sign the papers, right?

19:47.604 --> 19:51.107
Is that what you want?
Will that really make you happy?

19:51.858 --> 19:54.068
I don't know what the fuck
is going to make me happy now.

19:54.110 --> 19:56.529
But you leave me no choice.

19:56.571 --> 19:58.114
Okay.

20:00.617 --> 20:02.118
Are you sure?

20:12.420 --> 20:14.130
Let's see.

20:21.304 --> 20:23.139
I'm really sorry. Forgive me.

20:23.389 --> 20:26.559
Well, I don't give a fuck now.

20:26.601 --> 20:30.104
Make sure your boyfriend
signs the NDA

20:30.146 --> 20:33.107
and we'll be done
with the negotiation.

20:33.149 --> 20:34.609
You can take care of that.

20:34.651 --> 20:36.611
You can tell him and say goodbye,

20:36.653 --> 20:39.113
because I will keep seeing him.

20:40.657 --> 20:43.451
I think you misread this.

20:46.371 --> 20:49.165
The deal is invalid
if he doesn't sign.

20:49.666 --> 20:52.168
So you better go and try
to convince him.

20:53.378 --> 20:55.838
It won't be that difficult, huh?

20:55.880 --> 20:57.674
One more thing.

20:57.924 --> 21:01.135
Our lawyer...
isn't ours anymore.

21:01.177 --> 21:03.179
He's my lawyer.

21:05.682 --> 21:08.935
You know for who I'm really sorry?

21:08.977 --> 21:12.146
Not me, I'm better than ever.

21:12.188 --> 21:16.109
And I don't deserve that you say
for that bastard out there.

21:16.150 --> 21:21.197
No. For me.
I'm sorry for me.

21:21.489 --> 21:23.157
For both of us, actually.

21:23.199 --> 21:26.703
Because... we lost everything
we were.

21:27.704 --> 21:29.664
We got lost in this shit.

21:29.706 --> 21:30.873
And yes, I got swept up.

21:32.750 --> 21:34.669
You're really good.

21:34.711 --> 21:36.713
Did you notice just now?

21:37.213 --> 21:40.174
Hey, did you read
the last clause of the deal?

21:40.216 --> 21:42.218
Take a look.

21:45.888 --> 21:48.224
Son of a bitch!

22:01.738 --> 22:05.408
Hey girl.
Got available lots.

22:05.450 --> 22:07.118
