1:08:16.802 --> 1:08:18.762
to confirm everything
you just said.

1:08:18.804 --> 1:08:22.015
To be honest, Mr. Riscal,
your wife is your best hope

1:08:22.057 --> 1:08:24.768
to avoid being prosecuted
for attempted murder.

1:08:24.810 --> 1:08:26.978
The CCTV! There's CCTV!

1:08:27.020 --> 1:08:28.563
It must have been recorder,
you can verify there.

1:08:28.605 --> 1:08:32.275
We did, and nothing was recorded
from the last 24 hours.

1:08:32.317 --> 1:08:32.776
What?

1:08:32.818 --> 1:08:35.779
I'm assuming that after asking
your wife and your best friend

1:08:35.821 --> 1:08:39.825
to have intercourse, you didn't
want any recordings, right?

1:08:45.288 --> 1:08:47.207
Arrgh! It really hurts.

1:08:47.833 --> 1:08:49.292
Give me your belt.

1:08:49.334 --> 1:08:51.044
Cotiti, what the fuck is this?

1:08:51.086 --> 1:08:53.630
Baby, the belt.

1:08:57.092 --> 1:08:58.134
Raise your leg.

1:09:07.060 --> 1:09:09.312
Can someone explain
what the fuck is going on?

1:09:09.354 --> 1:09:12.357
Calm down, okay? We made a deal.

1:09:13.567 --> 1:09:14.985
One moment.

1:09:16.361 --> 1:09:20.365
Let's make a deal.

1:09:23.869 --> 1:09:26.371
One more time.

1:09:28.081 --> 1:09:30.333
The safe box code is...

1:09:30.375 --> 1:09:34.337
the date of our wedding,
03/06/13.

1:09:34.379 --> 1:09:36.840
Okay, what else?

1:09:36.882 --> 1:09:39.384
The security controls
are in the office.

1:09:39.634 --> 1:09:45.348
-The code is 8436... 19.
-36... 19. Great.

1:09:45.390 --> 1:09:48.852
You need to delete the last
24 hours and turn it off.

1:09:48.894 --> 1:09:50.395
Okay.

1:09:56.902 --> 1:09:59.404
I need you to wake him up.

1:10:00.196 --> 1:10:01.907
Do it.

1:10:27.933 --> 1:10:29.935
Hi, baby.

1:10:45.200 --> 1:10:46.910
Bingo.

1:11:23.989 --> 1:11:28.493
-Motherfucker! Hey!
-Cat, Cat, Cat!

1:11:33.999 --> 1:11:36.167
Fucking bitch.

1:11:36.209 --> 1:11:38.461
Fucking bitch.

1:11:38.503 --> 1:11:41.006
The gun was in the safe.

1:11:41.506 --> 1:11:44.509
Only she and I know the code.

1:11:49.514 --> 1:11:51.516
There it is.

1:11:51.558 --> 1:11:53.351
At the back.

1:11:58.023 --> 1:11:59.524
Okay.

1:12:01.026 --> 1:12:02.986
We will carry out
an investigation

1:12:03.028 --> 1:12:05.989
to confirm everything
you're saying.

1:12:06.031 --> 1:12:07.991
I want to speak with my wife.

1:12:08.033 --> 1:12:10.535
In due time, Mr. Riscal.

1:12:11.327 --> 1:12:12.996
Can I make a call?

1:12:13.038 --> 1:12:14.998
My advice is,
wait for your lawyer

1:12:15.040 --> 1:12:17.500
and he'll suggest what to do.

1:12:17.542 --> 1:12:19.544
Do you have a husband?

1:12:20.045 --> 1:12:22.047
Wife.

1:12:30.680 --> 1:12:32.265
3 DAYS LATER

1:13:10.095 --> 1:13:11.596
Get in.

1:13:47.423 --> 1:13:49.634
I talked to the police

1:13:53.638 --> 1:13:56.099
and told them that after dinner,

1:13:56.141 --> 1:14:00.145
a pair of burglars broke in
and pointed at us.

1:14:00.645 --> 1:14:03.606
They shot me in the leg,
and when you tried to protect me,

1:14:03.648 --> 1:14:07.152
they beat you up,
and you fell unconscious.

1:14:07.652 --> 1:14:11.156
What about Marcos? Where is he?

1:14:14.159 --> 1:14:16.911
-We need to take you to a hospital.
-Don't worry.

1:14:17.370 --> 1:14:18.913
I'm okay.

1:14:18.955 --> 1:14:24.377
Listen. Remember when you said
that you'd do anything for me?

1:14:24.419 --> 1:14:27.672
Of course I remember!

1:14:28.173 --> 1:14:30.633
That has nothing to do with this.
We need to call an ambulance.

1:14:30.675 --> 1:14:33.678
Relax. I'm fine.

1:14:37.182 --> 1:14:38.975
I'm sorry.

1:15:35.740 --> 1:15:40.745
You have 24 hours to sign.
Read it thoroughly.

1:15:40.995 --> 1:15:42.747
Take your time.

1:15:45.541 --> 1:15:49.254
Oh, and your lawyer,
our lawyer...

1:15:49.754 --> 1:15:52.257
is now my lawyer.

1:15:53.258 --> 1:15:58.221
This is a low blow, my father
thought of you as a friend.

1:15:58.263 --> 1:16:01.557
I wish he was alive
to see you as the snake you are.

1:16:38.803 --> 1:16:46.311
-Hello? This is a surprise.
-I need you. Urgently.

1:16:53.318 --> 1:16:54.986
Where are we going?

1:16:55.028 --> 1:16:57.322
Home, honey.

1:16:57.822 --> 1:16:59.824
We're going home.

1:17:35.860 --> 1:17:37.028
Good morning.

1:17:37.070 --> 1:17:39.781
-Morning, sir.
-I don't want any calls, please.

1:17:42.867 --> 1:17:44.869
It's been so long.

1:17:45.119 --> 1:17:49.832
Fantastic. Just a couple details,
but everything's okay.

1:17:49.874 --> 1:17:53.086
Love trumps again, right?

1:17:53.127 --> 1:17:56.339
That's crazy. Thank you.

1:17:56.381 --> 1:17:58.633
You don't have to thank me.

1:17:58.674 --> 1:18:00.301
You don't know what you
just avoided.

1:18:00.343 --> 1:18:01.844
Yes. Yes, I know.

1:18:01.886 --> 1:18:05.348
That's why I sent you an envelope
with the new deal

1:18:05.390 --> 1:18:07.642
and a copy of the proof

1:18:07.683 --> 1:18:09.644
of what really happened
that night.

1:18:09.685 --> 1:18:12.397
You don't want
the truth to be known, right?

1:18:12.647 --> 1:18:14.399
She would become
a murder suspect.

1:18:14.649 --> 1:18:18.861
-Hey, that wasn't the deal.
- Why, did we sign an agreement?

1:18:18.903 --> 1:18:20.363
Call me back when you read it.

1:18:20.405 --> 1:18:23.199
And don't worry,
if I fall, you all fall.
